  {
    "ID": 293418410,
    "key": "This fantastic concoction is the pinnacle of what research on human anatomy has yielded. The few who know of its existence claim that to consume it is to ascend to a higher state of being, something beyond a mere human.",
    "original": "This fantastic concoction is the pinnacle of what research on human anatomy has yielded. The few who know of its existence claim that to consume it is to ascend to a higher state of being, something beyond a mere human.",
    "translation": "这种神奇的混合物是人体解剖学研究成果的顶峰。很少有人知道它的存在，他们声称，喝下它就能让人升华到一种更高的境界，一种超越人类的东西。",
    "stage": 1,
    "context": "this.m.Description = 'This fantastic concoction is the pinnacle of what research on human anatomy has yielded. The few who know of its existence claim that to consume it is to ascend to a higher state of being, something beyond a mere human.'"
  },
